			"content_html": "<p><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2018/09/29/opinion/sunday/in-praise-of-mediocrity.html\">In Praise of Mediocrity - The New York Times</a> →</p>\n\n<p>Tim Wu on having hobbies:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Lost here is the gentle pursuit of a modest competence, the doing of something just because you enjoy it, not because you are good at it.</p>\n</blockquote>\n",
